{"tid":468786,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"區議員關注報道指有黑警虛報「處理違泊」　盧偉聰稱正調查","createTime":"2017-11-14T16:46:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-14T17:05:42.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d26b094ffab6cc69e7fcce1c47cfa9e74d6d7e43","tid":468786,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T16:46:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1364748-20171114.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1364748-20171114.htm&d=XH28pMGT6MRyCCb5fGXV9ZnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=8a4157c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1364748-20171114.htm&h=faf839c5\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1364748-20171114.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n警務處處長盧偉聰出席灣仔區議會會議，不少區議員關注區內的違法泊車和警方執法問題。<br />\n<br />\n區議員李均頤引述報道指兩名隸屬北角警區的警員，今年7月初被委派處理一宗違泊個案，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">但向上級虛報已到場處理，實際卻沒有到場。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n盧偉聰表示，警方非常重視事件，正進行全面調查和覆檢，如果發現有人需要就事件負責，一定會嚴肅跟進。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，違泊問題成因複雜，過去幾年警方發出的告票數目比前一年多，但問題似乎未見改善，警方正研究透過閉路電視片段加強執法，但由於涉及修改法律，未必能夠在短時間內落實有關措施。"},{"pid":"d5cdcb62c680b57a123c3a5a43ee526cf6dfca7b","tid":468786,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T16:48:20.000Z","msg":"黑警97後真係極速淪陷"},{"pid":"e4ac80fe05950b1a0e11d423b91e434d670a3ff9","tid":468786,"uid":55077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T17:05:42.000Z","msg":"常言道學壞三日，學好三年"}]}